verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, the expression levels of miR-29a, let-7a-2-3p and miR-140-5p were upregulated in the IUGR group (P = 0.0001, P = 0.0053 and P = 0.0033, respectively), whereas the expression levels of miR-126a-3p and miR-223-3p were downregulated (P = 0.0355 and P = 0.0261, respectively) in the IUGR group.
